{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after that, we got up in the morning, we stood in an appell, and then they gave us a little coffee and a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us to stay in line five in a row, and we were marching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where, we didn't know the first day where we're going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they took us in 187 or 185 steps down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was our-- a stone mine, whatever they called it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then one SS told us that-- to pick up a stone and to keep that stone between our legs, between our feet, and to wait.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So each one went there and picked up a stone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the meantime, the SS men went into the office and they had a cup of coffee, you know, and then we-- we picked up all our stones, and then we waited with our hands in the back.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he came and he checked if we-- each one took us enough big stone, you know, not-- not if we've committed sin, we take a small stone.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have to take a big stone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whoever he didn't like, he says, you didn't take a big stone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You didn't take enough big stone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You come with me!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He took him to the, uh, pile of stones, and he made him pick up a stone maybe bigger than he was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he couldn't pick it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So what happened is, come here!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was the guard on top in that little booth there, and he says, just like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Shot him!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Just like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shot him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Death right away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- and then we went unload the stones, now bring back the stones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So again, the same thing for about four, five times a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
